Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.59,0:00:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.60,0:00:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.71,0:00:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.92,0:00:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.72,0:00:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.44,0:01:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.75,0:01:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.45,0:01:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.79,0:01:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[零式系统]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.49,0:01:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是把战况里出现的一切资料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在即时运算后\N得出的庞大预测值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.73,0:01:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接反馈给驾驶员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.43,0:01:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾驶舱系统的俗称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这系统甚至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把驾驶员赶进极端状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.91,0:01:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实现完美的胜利\N结果连自己的死也不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.79,0:01:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在世界变得混沌的时代里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.86,0:01:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,存在了令人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.02,0:01:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为最强兵器的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是飞翼零式和次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.23,0:02:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十六话\N[山克王国崩溃]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的敌人不是OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.85,0:02:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.18,0:02:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进而是地球的支配阶级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.75,0:02:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽管如此，我们就要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.32,0:02:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和OZ的特列斯派联手吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先须要把宇宙抢回手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.66,0:02:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了那目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.56,0:02:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们也须要容纳旧联合的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帐!怎能和他们联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，和罗姆斐拉敌对的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不联手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.17,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就不能粉碎他们的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有何看法?迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.58,0:02:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉现在是真正敌人一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.41,0:02:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们、特列斯派和旧联合也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.92,0:02:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是\N打倒罗姆斐拉之后怎么办啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面有结论后再叫我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!迪欧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.89,0:03:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前，我会独自战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了打倒罗姆斐拉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫无结论啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.09,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正的和平是什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，当我没说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.79,0:03:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说了不像我的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪欧，要去看有趣的东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有趣的东西?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,散布在山克王国的边境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.38,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在周围的军事基地集结军力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.92,0:04:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有错，OZ…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.79,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉想消灭山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为攻进来只是时间的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.00,0:04:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我试试和迪尔麦优侯爵谈一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉当山克王国的是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.51,0:04:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只好战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.48,0:04:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国是完全和平主义国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.45,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以抛掉武器和没有战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.89,0:04:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和平世界为目标的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以做出那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.26,0:04:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就会失去山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，我会努力避免爆发战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白莉莉娜殿下的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:05:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现实里，罗姆斐拉军正要攻来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜正迷恋于理想中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在现今世界的形势里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.18,0:05:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义能达成吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你否定莉莉娜殿下的理想吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.66,0:05:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义是人的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有希望，人活不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.96,0:05:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你也有什么希望吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.47,0:05:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有的只是和支配战斗的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.17,0:05:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔怎么了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.04,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够的话，我希望他快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那声音是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他们看马格亚那队的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.99,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!这样下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.62,0:06:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奥达\N你带第三队绕去左翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.32,0:06:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.19,0:06:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.23,0:06:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是卡特尔少爷吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们恭候已久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.17,0:06:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有东西给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是来领取它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，一次歼灭他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,队…队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.95,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人转为反击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那部白色机体是…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹04?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备了!沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷，你没事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉席得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以来对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么，卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔少爷你救了我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.01,0:07:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们才要多谢你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，卡特尔少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.51,0:07:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又需要钢弹了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到我一定要做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百兽之王狮子\N和小丑少年的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那小丑好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就行了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.44,0:08:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，观众也好兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.55,0:09:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是特洛瓦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.95,0:09:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.42,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你在这里吗!其他人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.49,0:09:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛呢?不是和你一起吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.76,0:09:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是特洛瓦以前的朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.13,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他再没打算战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!究竟怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候，兹巴洛夫上级特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到罗姆斐拉财团的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.95,0:09:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正着手制造巨大宇宙战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉着征用宇宙的资源和人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而进行的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令卫星市民有很重的负担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，工程正在赶工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但制造这么巨大的战舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成还须要一段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别找藉口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.81,0:10:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们尽快须要新的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.98,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象征吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.11,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ现在没有代替特列斯的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后的OZ一定要藉着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.75,0:10:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量的象征令士兵团结起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而扰乱那团结的王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要被消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.79,0:10:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你指山克王国吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.60,0:10:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了OZ和平政策的证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国才有其存在意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.54,0:10:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但到了现在\N她只是我们的障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.51,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，换言之…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.54,0:10:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不服从罗姆斐拉财团的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.01,0:10:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经不可以存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令，MD包围部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.93,0:10:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始从山岳地带的边境进军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!本主力部队由海岸进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.90,0:11:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,占领的目标\N是山克王国的首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.74,0:11:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,边境的监视系统拍到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的MD部队的进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.31,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚接到迪尔麦优侯爵的联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说OZ会攻击不停收容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.42,0:11:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的逃兵和武装游击队的本国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.26,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到罗姆斐拉会做出这等事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.40,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国对现在的世界来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是和平的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.24,0:11:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你别怪责\N为了保护她而战的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.45,0:11:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帕根\N拜托你疏散学园的学生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行…!闭嘴!次代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.60,0:12:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,数量始终相差太远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.84,0:12:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!各机投下比尔哥部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体退到防卫线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,援军?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.46,0:13:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐\N我们总算及时赶到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔吗? 好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.57,0:13:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义的山克王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.14,0:13:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于也被战争的风暴牵连了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.88,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃乐丝\N你没遵从柏根的指示吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.35,0:14:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这局势如果我不看到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来到山克王国就毫无意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会怎么办?莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抗战到底吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.46,0:14:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向友好国家要求军事援助吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.33,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国不能用这种方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.64,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，还有什么其他方法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.18,0:14:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果山克王国就此灭亡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会化为梦想消失呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人渴望的是真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了保护那和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.76,0:14:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家漂亮地在战斗\N非常美丽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.79,0:15:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!你太深入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.49,0:15:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别离开首都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.16,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我再次失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就无人能够阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.47,0:15:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没时间奉陪你好战的兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下你好狡猾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狡猾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.84,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以什么和平的\N甜言蜜语召集大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.31,0:15:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紧急关头时\N自己却什么也不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.65,0:15:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并非不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.35,0:15:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，只是做不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.75,0:15:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为什么完全和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本就不可能实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的老师曾这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.36,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类是好战的动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.53,0:15:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，由战胜的人支配就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:16:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样，秩序才会建立吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.30,0:16:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根据那想法及秩序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会产生和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若根据这想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.14,0:16:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们正朝着建立秩序在行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.28,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在现今有战争的这世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.18,0:16:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不战斗的完全和平主义\N有何作为?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是脱离现实之谈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.81,0:16:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经无路可退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以让他们冲破这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增…增援部队吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.42,0:16:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,区区这点攻击!别怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.19,0:16:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,诺茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.30,0:17:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道市区受到攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.98,0:17:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么也做不到的完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在没希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只会成为好战动物的食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在应该战斗啊，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.95,0:17:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类是好战动物也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.19,0:17:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不认为这样就没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信人类能选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.99,0:17:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不战斗实现和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满怀理想的莉莉娜殿下\N真美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.80,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的莉莉娜殿下只要说一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.24,0:17:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不满特列斯派或OZ的士兵们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.81,0:17:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会马上赶来这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.33,0:18:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然山克王国和我会挑起战火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.97,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，我就从我做得到的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝着完全和平踏出新的一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.14,0:18:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，首先要行动，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市区被攻击?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，遵照你的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.00,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我接上经由宇宙至
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,财团高层的个人线路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，现在的财团里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会有救助莉莉娜殿下的人吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.78,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王国的代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.58,0:19:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.38,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，本国因为OZ的宣战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入战斗状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.16,0:19:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自作聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.39,0:19:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算向别国要求军事援助吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿起武器战斗并非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.79,0:19:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提倡和平主义的山克王国所愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.83,0:19:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，既然本国成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ发动战争的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国就放弃主权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.87,0:19:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自动解体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.64,0:19:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要及时赶到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.55,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无论有任何理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.02,0:19:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不可以寻求以战斗解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.62,0:19:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本人也会由OZ看管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.39,0:19:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我对和平的理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.16,0:19:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.37,0:19:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这力量能作为罗姆斐拉向心力吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经没有战斗的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.58,0:20:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厉害!真厉害!莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用再挖苦我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我愈来愈喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.13,0:20:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你带路前去罗姆斐拉财团
